ActFirearms Act
SubjectUnited States Enforcement Officers Exemption Order, 2023 (Multi-modal Transportation of Firearms)
PrecisOrder making the UNITED STATES ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS EXEMPTION ORDER, 2023 (MULTI-MODAL TRANSPORTATION OF FIREARMS) in order to allow for United States Border Patrol and National Park Service officers to transit through the Waterton Lakes National Park (Alberta) and the E.C. Manning Provincial Park (British Columbia) with their duty firearms.
